function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.1.24') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.1.24!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (!is_file('TODO')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: TODO');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('TODO')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): TODO');
	} else if (sha1_file('TODO') != '61a0b9aea0212721df9a58b021fc90bcf8d271ed') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): TODO');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('TODO', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of TODO');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '61a0b9aea0212721df9a58b021fc90bcf8d271ed') {
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '5d74d5325ef7856a8359666d7c14624e52d7eee2') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '61a0b9aea0212721df9a58b021fc90bcf8d271ed') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('changelog.json.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of changelog.json.php');
	}

	if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== 'd5c470c77bcbc5ea7d51442d888aa5b86d1c67ed') {

			if (!@copy('changelog.json.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();

			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	writefile_5();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') != '6b31559ac21ba70ac7a415fbf5e6a4ed8122ea28') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') !== '6b31559ac21ba70ac7a415fbf5e6a4ed8122ea28') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') !== '8fd3f98696b108b13bd1385078a4f01162536ab9') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_5();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') !== '6b31559ac21ba70ac7a415fbf5e6a4ed8122ea28') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_6();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != '6041d3da6905b9da771a015f0fc5f8b36b6fe1c3') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '6041d3da6905b9da771a015f0fc5f8b36b6fe1c3') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'edf8fe38d3f9ce01fa1a16a0da0f41bb06c1a99b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_6();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '6041d3da6905b9da771a015f0fc5f8b36b6fe1c3') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
	writefile_8();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php') != 'd234b6a5a80434b6a296217e8df9bb7ce11ca129') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php') !== 'd234b6a5a80434b6a296217e8df9bb7ce11ca129') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php') !== '8bbd2cfff1958d4df5553d5bef84ab23c05ec36c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_8();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php') !== 'd234b6a5a80434b6a296217e8df9bb7ce11ca129') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
		}
	}

		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/oid/OIDplusOid.class.php');

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php');
	writefile_19();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php') != '1010cb902efbdf59f59f269cda520d8deb52a0f4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php') !== '1010cb902efbdf59f59f269cda520d8deb52a0f4') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php') !== 'b6f5840940a1357cf0988e70610e1e36f9493e9e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php') !== '1010cb902efbdf59f59f269cda520d8deb52a0f4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php');

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/x500dn/OIDplusX500DN.class.php');

		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/x500dn/OIDplusX500DN.class.php');

if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: setup/index.php');
	writefile_25();
	if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('setup/index.php') != '78b292cbe499d029d889b759b47efe36de8286c8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== '78b292cbe499d029d889b759b47efe36de8286c8') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== 'eaadef87cf65733a96c3dd177df5c32a7c61de95') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_25();
		if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== '78b292cbe499d029d889b759b47efe36de8286c8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): setup/index.php');
		}
	}
}
